abstract: The center and the New York Philharmonic announced they would seek simpler ways to improve a hall they have long wanted to change.
snippet: The center and the New York Philharmonic announced they would seek simpler ways to improve a hall they have long wanted to change.
lead_paragraph: One of the biggest cultural building projects in the country was sent back to the drawing board on Tuesday, when the new leaders of Lincoln Center and the New York Philharmonic announced they were scuttling a half-billion-dollar plan for a gut renovation of David Geffen Hall and seeking simpler ways to improve the lackluster theater.

abstract: Cynthia Brann will become the new correction commissioner in New York, disappointing some who wanted an outside set of eyes on a troubled agency.
snippet: Cynthia Brann will become the new correction commissioner in New York, disappointing some who wanted an outside set of eyes on a troubled agency.
lead_paragraph: After months of searching around the country for a new correction commissioner, Mayor Bill de Blasio announced on Tuesday that he had found the person to head the Correction Department, which oversees the troubled Rikers Island jail complex, from within its own ranks.

abstract: The SpaceX founder insists that he can ferry cargo into space and fly people anywhere in the world in less than an hour, and make money doing it.
snippet: The SpaceX founder insists that he can ferry cargo into space and fly people anywhere in the world in less than an hour, and make money doing it.
lead_paragraph: Elon Musk has finally explained how SpaceX could make money: through a rocket that can both deliver goods to space and fly people from New York to Shanghai in 39 minutes.

abstract: President Trump and Congress are turning their legislative focus to a sweeping change of the tax code. A 20 percent corporate rate is among the proposals.
snippet: President Trump and Congress are turning their legislative focus to a sweeping change of the tax code. A 20 percent corporate rate is among the proposals.
lead_paragraph: Today, President Trump and Congress will officially make a tax overhaul their big priority. The president will begin laying out at least some details in a speech in Indiana.

abstract: Temasek of Singapore is set to take a minority stake in CAA, as it competes to expand globally and into the digital realm.
snippet: Temasek of Singapore is set to take a minority stake in CAA, as it competes to expand globally and into the digital realm.
lead_paragraph: The Singaporean sovereign wealth fund Temasek will take a minority stake in the talent agency CAA, in a deal expected to be announced today, DealBook is the first to report. TPG Capital will remain the agencyâ€™s biggest shareholder.
